The Phone App
•
The Phone App is the new way of marrying local phone dealers with large
distributors. Local phone dealers can buy equipment they need at the right
price.
The large phone distributors can sell their equipment at much
greater margins with their payments guaranteed
•
The Phone App will be the middleman in the transaction which makes
buying wholesale cellular phone and accessories as easy as pressing a
button.
•
The Phone App will be EASY to use.
